uantum algorithm), to a class of theories\nsatisfying certain postulates allowing the formulation of a generalized notion\nof query algorithm, actually applies in the Jordan-algebraic setting where\nhigher-order interference is not possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Apr 2019 21:54:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
