ce the cooperation and may help controlling the air\nquality. The designed system helps the environmental agencies to assess their\nair pollution controlling policies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 12:24:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-12"}
